title: UFYB 14: Money Mindset Mistakes
itunes:title: Money Mindset Mistakes
description:
On this episode, I want to dig into the reasons why we have a poor relationship with money and share my personal story of how I shifted my money beliefs through coaching. Join me as I share the most important money mind shifts that you can implement to become more successful in your business and your career.

Get full show notes and more information here: https://unfckyourbrain.com/14
